<pb n="1071c" id="T55.2164.1071c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1071c01" ed="T"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="1071c02" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 2164</head>
<lb n="1071c03" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="1" type="卷"/><note n="1071046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】鎌倉時代寫高山寺藏本，【甲】享保二年寫大谷大學藏本，【乙】大日本佛教全書，【丙】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本</note><jhead>靈巖<note n="1071047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔寺〕－【丙】</note><app n="1071047"><lem>寺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="1071048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（（和尚…等））九字＝（（圓行和尚））四字【甲】【丙】</note><app word-count="9" n="1071048"><lem>和尚請來法門道具等</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">圓行和尚</rdg></app>
<lb n="1071c04" ed="T"/>目錄</jhead></juan>
<lb n="1071c05" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1071c06" ed="T"/><div1 type="xu"><mulu level="1" label="上表" type="序"/><p id="pT55p1071c0601">入唐還學沙門<note n="1071049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔圓行言〕－【甲】</note><app n="1071049"><lem>圓行言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>。圓行載次戊午。銜命
<lb n="1071c07" ed="T"/>請益之列。訪道西海之外。其年臘月得到長
<lb n="1071c08" ed="T"/>安<note n="1071050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔城〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1071050"><lem>城</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>。歲次己未正月十<note n="1071051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三＝二&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1071051"><lem>三</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">二</rdg></app>日。依奏奉&CB00330;住
<lb n="1071c09" ed="T"/>青龍寺。幸遇彼寺灌頂教主法<note n="1071052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">號＝蹄【丙】</note><app n="1071052"><lem>號</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">蹄</rdg></app>義真和尚
<lb n="1071c10" ed="T"/>以為師主。其大<note n="1071053" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔威〕－【甲】【丙】</note><app n="1071053"><lem>威</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>德則惠果阿闍梨弟子同
<lb n="1071c11" ed="T"/>門義操和尚付法之弟子也。明閑<note n="1071054" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三＝二【丙】</note><app n="1071054"><lem>三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">二</rdg></app>教。妙通
<lb n="1071c12" ed="T"/>五部。法之<note n="1071055" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">棟梁＝所歸【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1071055"><lem>棟梁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">所歸</rdg></app>。國之所<note n="1071056" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔歸〕&M062403;－【乙】，歸＝師【丙】</note><app n="1071056"><lem>歸</lem><rdg resp="【乙】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">師</rdg></app>圓行幸賴聖朝
<lb n="1071c13" ed="T"/>之鴻恩。師主之深慈。決疑兩部之大法。開悟
<lb n="1071c14" ed="T"/>諸尊之密法。閏正月二日蒙授阿闍梨位灌
<lb n="1071c15" ed="T"/>頂也。左街功德使并僧錄和尚供奉大德金
<lb n="1071c16" ed="T"/>剛門<note n="1071057" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">徒＝從【丙】</note><app n="1071057"><lem>徒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">從</rdg></app>悉集道場共致隨喜。斯法也觀心月
<lb n="1071c17" ed="T"/>輪則居住凡位<note n="1071058" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">備＝脩【丙】</note><app n="1071058"><lem>備</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">脩</rdg></app>佛陀之德。誦口密言則不
<lb n="1071c18" ed="T"/>逕長劫頓登<note n="1071059" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">大＝天【乙】</note><app n="1071059"><lem>大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">天</rdg></app>覺之位。故龍樹<note n="1071060" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔言〕－【乙】</note><app n="1071060"><lem>言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>。乘羊而
<lb n="1071c19" ed="T"/>行。<note n="1071061" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">願＝顯【乙】，頓&M062485;【乙】</note><note n="1071061" resp="CBETA" type="mod">願＝顯【乙】，＝頓&M062485;【乙】</note><app n="1071061"><lem><sic resp="【乙】" corr="頓">願</sic></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">顯</rdg></app><note n="1071062" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">難＋（難）【乙】</note><app n="1071062"><lem>難</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">難難</rdg></app>致遠策馬而馳漸期差疾。乘神通
<lb n="1071c20" ed="T"/>行發念則到。是則顯密之別<note n="1071063" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">也＝色【乙】</note><app n="1071063"><lem>也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">色</rdg></app>。亦祕密經
<lb n="1071c21" ed="T"/>言。一善男子建立道場修念三密。其國界內
<lb n="1071c22" ed="T"/>無七難災。國<note n="1071064" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">王＝主【甲】</note><app n="1071064"><lem>王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">主</rdg></app>大臣<note n="1071065" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">日日＝月日【丙】</note><app n="1071065"><lem>日日</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">月日</rdg></app>增長福壽。是則
<pb n="1072a" id="T55.2164.1072a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1072a01" ed="T"/>真言之功矣。雖然波浪沷漢。風雨漂舶。越彼
<lb n="1072a02" ed="T"/>鯨海平歸聖境。是則聖力之所能也。伏惟皇
<lb n="1072a03" ed="T"/>帝陛下功超<note n="1072001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">玄＝立【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1072001"><lem>玄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">立</rdg></app>極道<note n="1072002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">冠＝&CB00018;【甲】</note><app n="1072002"><lem>冠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&CB00018;</rdg></app>混<note n="1072003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">元＝無【丙】</note><app n="1072003"><lem>元</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">無</rdg></app>。讚堯寶圖。復
<lb n="1072a04" ed="T"/>禹<note n="1072004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">丕續＝丕績【甲】【丙】，不請【乙】</note><note n="1072004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">丕續＝丕績【甲】【丙】，＝不請【乙】</note><app n="1072004"><lem>丕續</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">丕績</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">不請</rdg></app>。悲蒼生而濡足。鍾佛囑而<note n="1072005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">垂＝乘【丙】</note><app n="1072005"><lem>垂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">乘</rdg></app>衣。以
<lb n="1072a05" ed="T"/>陛下興隆佛法。沒馱之舍利浸波遠來。以陛
<lb n="1072a06" ed="T"/>下慈育海內。祕密之經法過海遙到也。祕法
<lb n="1072a07" ed="T"/>傳來非<note n="1072006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">是＝只【甲】，是＋（足）【丙】</note><app n="1072006"><lem>是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">只</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">是足</rdg></app>無以也。如來本有福智之力。法界
<lb n="1072a08" ed="T"/>本性加持之力矣。大日如來。金剛薩埵。龍猛
<lb n="1072a09" ed="T"/>菩薩。龍智菩薩。金<note n="1072007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">剛＋（智）【丙】</note><app n="1072007"><lem>剛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">剛智</rdg></app>三藏。不空三藏。惠果
<lb n="1072a10" ed="T"/>和尚。義操和尚。義真和尚。次第相傳。即授圓
<lb n="1072a11" ed="T"/>行。所授經法舍利道具等目錄在別。謹以奉
<lb n="1072a12" ed="T"/>進輕黷威嚴伏增戰越。沙門圓行誠恐誠惶
<lb n="1072a13" ed="T"/>謹言。</p>
<lb n="1072a14" ed="T"/><p id="pT55p1072a1401" rend="margin-left:2em">承和六年十二月十九日入唐還學沙門
<lb n="1072a15" ed="T"/>傳燈大法師位圓行上表</p></div1>
