<lb n="1072a19" ed="T"/><list><item id="itemT55p1072a1901"><note n="1072011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（新請…卷）十六字∞（梵字…卷）六字【甲】</note><note n="1072011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（新請來真言經法都二十六部三十三卷）十六字∞（梵字三部四卷）六字【甲】</note><app n="1072011"><lem>新請來真言經法。<note n="1072012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">都＋（合）【甲】【丙】</note><app n="1072012"><lem>都</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">都合</rdg></app>二十六部三十三卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">梵字三部四卷</rdg></app></item>
<lb n="1072a20" ed="T"/><item id="itemT55p1072a2001"><note n="1072013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（新請…卷）十六字∞（梵字…卷）六字【甲】</note><note n="1072013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（新請來真言經法都二十六部三十三卷）十六字∞（梵字三部四卷）六字【甲】</note><app n="1072013"><lem>梵字三部四卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">新請來真言經法都二十六部三十三卷</rdg></app></item>
<lb n="1072a21" ed="T"/><item id="itemT55p1072a2101">顯教經論疏章等。都四十部八十八卷
<lb n="1072a22" ed="T"/><p id="pT55p1072a2201" rend="margin-left:2em">已上三種。總六十九部一百二十<note n="1072014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三＝五【丙】</note><app n="1072014"><lem>三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">五</rdg></app>卷。</p></item>
<lb n="1072a23" ed="T"/><item id="itemT55p1072a2301">佛舍利都三千餘粒</item>
<lb n="1072a24" ed="T"/><item id="itemT55p1072a2401">付屬物三種</item>
<lb n="1072a25" ed="T"/><item id="itemT55p1072a2501">佛像曼荼<note n="1072015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔羅〕－【丙】</note><app n="1072015"><lem>羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>圖樣都十二種</item>
<lb n="1072a26" ed="T"/><item id="itemT55p1072a2601">道具都十六箇</item></list></div1>
