<lb n="1072a28" ed="T"/><list><item id="itemT55p1072a2801"><title>奇特最勝金輪佛頂念儀軌一卷</title></item>
<lb n="1072a29" ed="T"/><item id="itemT55p1072a2901"><title>白傘蓋佛頂儀軌一卷</title></item>
<pb n="1072b" id="T55.2164.1072b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1072b01" ed="T"/><item id="itemT55p1072b0101"><title>一字頂輪王念誦儀軌一卷</title><note place="inline">依忉利天王宮會所說經譯</note></item>
<lb n="1072b02" ed="T"/><item id="itemT55p1072b0201"><title>蘇悉地法</title>一部二卷</item>
<lb n="1072b03" ed="T"/><item id="itemT55p1072b0301"><title>諸佛境界<note n="1072016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">攝＝樣【甲】</note><app n="1072016"><lem>攝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">樣</rdg></app>真實經</title>一部三卷<note place="inline">般若三藏譯</note></item>
<lb n="1072b04" ed="T"/><item id="itemT55p1072b0401"><title>降三世儀軌一卷</title><note place="inline">遍智阿闍梨指授</note></item>
<lb n="1072b05" ed="T"/><item id="itemT55p1072b0501"><title>與金剛弟子入壇受灌頂法經一卷</title></item>
