<lb n="1073c16" ed="T"/><p id="pT55p1073c1601" rend="margin-left:4em">入唐沙門傳燈大法<note n="1073052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">師＋（位）【甲】【丙】</note><app n="1073052"><lem>師</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">師位</rdg></app>圓行<note place="inline">上</note>。</p>
<lb n="1073c17" ed="T"/><p id="pT55p1073c1701"><note n="1073053" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以下高山寺本無之今依甲本補載以乙丙二本對校之</note>右街僧錄三教講論大德沙門體<note n="1073054" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">虛＝處【丙】</note><app n="1073054"><lem>虛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">處</rdg></app>。奉本
<lb n="1073c18" ed="T"/>使<note n="1073055" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">仇＝仉【丙】</note><app n="1073055"><lem>仇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">仉</rdg></app>驃騎<note n="1073056" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">怗＝帖差【丙】</note><app n="1073056"><lem>怗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">帖差</rdg></app>三覺供奉大德六人就青龍寺
<lb n="1073c19" ed="T"/>與日本國傳燈大法師位圓行語論本教玄理
<lb n="1073c20" ed="T"/>具名如後。</p>
<lb n="1073c21" ed="T"/><p id="pT55p1073c2101" rend="margin-left:3em">保壽寺內供奉臨壇大德沙門常辨。</p>
<lb n="1073c22" ed="T"/><p id="pT55p1073c2201" rend="margin-left:3em">章敬寺內供奉禪宗大德沙門<note n="1073057" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">弘＝和【丙】</note><app n="1073057"><lem>弘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">和</rdg></app>辨。</p>
<pb n="1074a" id="T55.2164.1074a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1074a01" ed="T"/><p id="pT55p1074a0101" rend="margin-left:3em">招福寺內供奉講論大德沙門齊<note n="1074001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">高＝亮【丙】</note><app n="1074001"><lem>高</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">亮</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="1074a02" ed="T"/><p id="pT55p1074a0201" rend="margin-left:3em">興唐寺內供奉講論大德沙門<note n="1074002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">光顥＝先顯【丙】</note><app n="1074002"><lem>光顥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">先顯</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="1074a03" ed="T"/><p id="pT55p1074a0301" rend="margin-left:3em">雲花寺內供奉講論大德沙門海岸。</p>
<lb n="1074a04" ed="T"/><p id="pT55p1074a0401" rend="margin-left:3em">青龍寺內供奉講論大德沙門圓鏡。</p>
<lb n="1074a05" ed="T"/><p id="pT55p1074a0501">右件大德等所與圓行大德語論教門策目並
<lb n="1074a06" ed="T"/>錄申<note n="1074003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">聞＝問【丙】</note><app n="1074003"><lem>聞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">問</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="1074a07" ed="T"/><p id="pT55p1074a0701" rend="margin-left:2em">開成四年正月十五日。</p></item></list></div1>
